(40, 23, 23, 40, 9, 13, 13, 'mercy', 'Mercy Over Sacrifice', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of mercy over ritual practices. Matthew 23:23 critiques the focus on minor tithes while neglecting weightier matters like mercy, which is echoed in Matthew 9:13''s declaration of valuing mercy over sacrifice.', 'theme', 0.419, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 23, 23, 40, 5, 19, 20, 'weightier matters of the law', 'Righteousness and Weightier Matters', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of true righteousness over mere ritual observance. Matthew 23:23 critiques the Pharisees for neglecting ''weightier matters,'' while Matthew 5:20 calls for a righteousness that exceeds theirs.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 23, 23, 9, 15, 22, 22, 'weightier matters of the law', 'Obedience Over Rituals', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of prioritizing obedience and moral integrity over mere ritualistic practices. Matthew highlights the weightier matters of the law, while Samuel underscores that obedience is better than sacrifice.', 'theme', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 23, 23, 20, 21, 3, 3, 'judgment, mercy, and faith', 'Justice Over Ritual Sacrifice', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of justice and judgment over mere ritual practices. Matthew highlights the weightier matters of the law, while Proverbs states that doing justice is more acceptable than sacrifice.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
